final currentMatches = state is MatchListLoadSuccess && cursor != null\\n       
  ? (state as MatchListLoadSuccess).matches\\n          : <Map<String, dynamic>>
[];\\n      emit(MatchListLoadSuccess(\\n        matches: [...currentMatches, ..
.items],\\n        hasMore: result[\'has_more\'] as bool? ?? false,\\n        ne
xtCursor: result[\'next_cursor\'] as String?,\\n      ));\\n    } on Exception c
atch (e) {\\n      emit(MatchListLoadFailure(e.toString()));\\n    }\\n  }\\n  `
``\\n- **依据**: PRD `v1-matching.md` 第 192-195 行要求游标分页；当前实现不符合
分页追加预期。\\n\\n### 6. 后端单元测试覆盖不足\\n- **位置**: `apps/api/src/modu
